    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You and your tapes have landed on a strange planet...</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, you need to find all to get back home and continue your mission. But the planet is in its final days, and it's up to you to decide: save the planet... or ignore everything and stick to your mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meanwhile, you can make (or break) some gothic friendships along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208680/extras/2384f8865c1eb5bd61a46819e68b6381.webp?t=1764091756\" width=32 height=18 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT TO EXPECT?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pineapple:</strong> Hard to explain, better to see for yourself. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Exploration:</strong> Just a strange planet.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rednecks:</strong> Ahhh, what a mess!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Humor:</strong> Silly, but it’ll make you laugh, lol.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Adventure:</strong>  Very cool.. I THINK.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demonic lawyers:</strong> Or something like that...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A parry-based RPG.<br>You'll need to defend at the right moment to avoid damage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208680/extras/26f6ff6b6d1ef95c580fdf261c62e90b.apng?t=1764091756\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208680/extras/26f6ff6b6d1ef95c580fdf261c62e90b.poster.avif?t=1764091756\" class=\"bb_